21#include "mpc-impl.h"
22
23mpfr_prec_t
24mpc_get_prec (mpc_srcptr x)
25{
26 mpfr_prec_t precre = MPC_PREC_RE (x);
27 return (MPC_PREC_IM (x) == precre ? precre : 0);
28}
